  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a copper pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the bruised lemongrass stalks and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the boneless chicken breast pieces and cook until browned.",
    "Add the shaved bonito flakes and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the tomato puree and chicken broth, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until the chicken is cooked through.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and garnish with additional lemongrass stalks if desired."
